latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Do you strive to live,
Or you just exist. 

Your soul dying inside the coffin of your body,
Or is it alive in your heart? 

Your life consuming you,
Or you consuming all your life?
By feeling things you never felt,
By embedding new experiences and memories in your shell,
By thinking about the things you never tell,
By ageing your body's every single cell. 

Does it make you go crazy,
Or make you sane?
Does it make you lose,
Or make you gain? 

Does it make you your own master,
Or make you your own slave?
What do you accept,
And whom do you blame? 

What do you want to sacrifice,
And what do you want to save?
Does it make you stand,
Or make you lie on an empty plane? 

Does it make you laugh,
Or make you cry?
Does it make you fall,
Or make you fly? 

Does it make you hate,
Or make you love?
Does it make you feel,
Or make you numb? 

Does it make you close your eyes,
Or open them wide?
Does it give you the reasons to live,
Or the reasons to die? 

Is it bright like the sun,
Or dull like the moon? 
Is it a bane,
or a boon?

 ~Dakshita Vadhera
